summary: I have done my very best to improve the life of my maid.  The Maid has a very bad habit of leaving me during the warm months for several days.  However, she has begun to realize I need someone to supervise.  She allows me to train other novice maids in her absence. This increased responsibility has shown me that I have many talents to share.  I believe the world is ready for all I have to offer.

profile_positions.description: I am the Queen of the Castle.  All employees must do my bidding, when I want, how I want.  It does not matter if I wanted it one way yesterday, today I may want it another way. I am the Queen and that is the way it should be. I hear there is another woman in a place called London, England who also calls herself Queen.  I cannot confirm her existence.  You are safe to assume that I am the only Queen that matters.
profile_positions.title: Queen of the House

profile_positions.description:
During my time as Master At Hard to Get, I have been able to make everyone think they want to pet me.  However, hands are not my thing.  People may only touch me with their feet, unless I *really* want something or I'm ill.  I have successfully conned many guests to Around My Castle into thinking I want them to pet me.  Every once in a while I do allow humans to pet or brush me.  I have found this lulls them into compliance and gives them a false sense of belonging and deserving of Queen love.  
***Disclaimer*** There have been rumors that I enjoy belly pets and have even been known to drool when over relaxed.  These are mere rumors.
profile_positions.title: Master at Hard To Get

profile_positions.description: You may think you know which litter box I prefer.  However, you would be wrong.  You may think I would use one of my three litter boxes, again you would be wrong.  I have successfully trained The Maid to put down pee pads and to pick the pile of feces off the floor.  I currently require three different litter boxes, three different types of litter, "puppy" training pads in front of each litter box, a garbage bag under one litter box, a washing machine tray under another, and finally a "puppy" training pad holder.   still do not comply with The Maid's wishes and demands.
profile_positions.title: Master of Finky

profile_positions.description: To ensure The Maid awakes on time, I sing her the song of my people.  To keep her on her toes, I frequently change my mind and routine.  I may feel the spirit move me at 3:30 am or I may feel it at 10 am.  However, it is a lovely song, so she should enjoy regardless of when I perform.  As she falls asleep at night I will often sing The Maid a song of my people, very loudly and from far away.  This is the lullaby from the most advanced species in the universe, cats.  The Maid should consider this part of her benefit package.
profile_positions.title: Lead Singer

profile_positions.description: I have been perfecting my motivational stare.  With just a look I am able to obtain food, ice in my water, more dry food, foot petting, people leaving me alone.  The list continues.
profile_positions.title: Queen of Stares

profile_positions.description:
Besides the fact that my mere presence in a room is enough, I also know how to decorate a room.  Every time I enter a room I leave a little decoration.  I have been known to leave piles of fur, a whisker, and the occasional claw around the house.  When I feel a room is in desperate need of improvement I even leave a hairball, a pile of vomit, or a trail of vomit. With these decorations I do my best work at night so that it can be discovered in the morning.  
I have also been known to go to extreme measures- urinating on the carpet enough times so that The Maid had to replace the rug.  Honestly, it did not go with the decor.
profile_positions.title: Professional Home Decorator

profile_positions.description:
I have a psychic ability related to suitcases.  The large purple one means The Maid will be gone at least 7 nights and will hire an Apprentice Maid.  This usually happens twice a year (one when the weather in warmer and one when there is the cold white stuff on the ground).  The multi colored one means 3 - 6 nights.  The Maid will usually hire an Apprentice Maid.  This happens more frequently and at various times of the year.  Then there is a dark blue one.  This means The Maid is leaving for 2-3 nights. If there is white stuff on the ground, she will hire an Apprentice Maid.  If there is no white stuff, Older Maid will stop by to meet my needs.  Older Maid is nice and comes by even when The Maid is not here, but that's something else.  She smells kind of like The Maid, but different, too.  
If you need suitcase psychic abilities, I am available.
profile_positions.title: Suitcase Psychic
